1
00:00:24,980 --> 00:00:28,500
♪Heavens strike with thunderous wrath♪

2
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:32,180
♪Mountains and rivers shatter before my eyes♪

3
00:00:32,420 --> 00:00:35,500
♪Endless splendor cultivated through lifetimes♪

4
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:39,220
♪Turns to dust between my fingers in an instant♪

5
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:44,100
♪When the line between good and evil is clear♪

6
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:47,780
♪Countless souls drift into the boundless wilds♪

7
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:51,340
♪Carrying the spirit fire forward♪

8
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,340
♪I defy fate♪

9
00:00:53,580 --> 00:00:56,460
♪Just to remain by your side♪

10
00:00:57,340 --> 00:01:00,740
♪Falling into love's abyss♪

11
00:01:01,180 --> 00:01:04,420
♪Like heavy rain pouring down♪

12
00:01:04,860 --> 00:01:08,300
♪Drunk on romance♪

13
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:11,980
♪In a blink, love and hate vanish into illusion♪

14
00:01:12,700 --> 00:01:16,060
♪Falling into endless love♪

15
00:01:16,500 --> 00:01:19,340
♪Stirring waves upending a lifetime♪

16
00:01:19,620 --> 00:01:22,420
♪Even if this life leads to ruin♪

17
00:01:22,860 --> 00:01:26,460
♪I still choose to be entangled with you♪

18
00:01:27,020 --> 00:01:30,100
♪Through all lifetimes♪

19
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:33,100
[When Destiny Brings The Demon]

20
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:36,500
[Based on the JJWXC novel "When Destiny Brings The Demon" by Fu Hua]

21
00:01:36,620 --> 00:01:39,500
[Episode 14]
["Roleplay" Amidst Peril]

22
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:45,220
I heard they vanished here.

23
00:02:05,750 --> 00:02:06,940
So much blood was spilled.

24
00:02:07,670 --> 00:02:10,060
Seems like Sima Jiao is severely hurt.

25
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,810
Master Yuan, there are bloodstains here.

26
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,500
Let's follow the blood trail.

27
00:02:23,320 --> 00:02:24,530
They came here too.

28
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:27,970
The blood suddenly vanishes here.

29
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:29,250
How strange.

30
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:30,410
Looks like

31
00:02:31,870 --> 00:02:33,220
we can no longer track

32
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,220
Sima Jiao's whereabouts.

33
00:02:34,830 --> 00:02:36,650
He must have used some secret spell.

34
00:02:37,270 --> 00:02:38,740
We must search harder.

35
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:42,090
Sima Jiao slaughtered countless innocents

36
00:02:42,550 --> 00:02:44,090
at Chiyan City and Baifeng Mountain.

37
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,300
If we don't seal him now,

38
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:47,780
he will massacre again

39
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,460
when he recovers.

40
00:02:49,990 --> 00:02:51,020
Indeed,

41
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,090
but staying here is pointless.

42
00:02:53,670 --> 00:02:56,500
I think we should return and discuss

43
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,410
with the other palace heads.

44
00:02:58,110 --> 00:02:58,740
Let's go.

45
00:03:08,990 --> 00:03:11,220
Using Tingyan's extreme-cold nature is hopeless.

46
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,300
I can't take her core and harm her.

47
00:03:13,990 --> 00:03:15,460
To break the Immortal-Demon Barrier,

48
00:03:15,870 --> 00:03:17,090
there's only one way left.

49
00:03:17,670 --> 00:03:19,130
Kill Sima Jiao.

50
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:20,780
When the Spirit Fire dies,

51
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,650
the barrier breaks.

52
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:23,690
He was too strong before.

53
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:24,740
I couldn't strike.

54
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:27,130
Now, he's gravely wounded

55
00:03:27,150 --> 00:03:27,940
and alone.

56
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,020
If I find allies,

57
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,130
I may succeed.

58
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:42,970
What are you afraid of?

59
00:03:43,110 --> 00:03:44,650
You tell me.

60
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,500
Grandmaster, spare me.

61
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,340
I can't take it anymore.

62
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:52,020
No mercy.

63
00:03:53,870 --> 00:03:54,500
What?

64
00:03:55,270 --> 00:03:55,940
You dislike it?

65
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:00,900
I dislike it.

66
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:07,220
Looks like you're indeed severely hurt.

67
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:09,780
Even the Truth Spell failed.

68
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:15,850
You said

69
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,420
you dislike it.

70
00:04:20,150 --> 00:04:21,570
Do you actually like it?

71
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:25,100
Why force me to speak the truth?

72
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,420
There are many ways

73
00:04:28,030 --> 00:04:29,010
to know what a person truly feels.

74
00:04:29,710 --> 00:04:30,860
Without Truth Spell,

75
00:04:32,350 --> 00:04:33,890
I can still sense

76
00:04:34,910 --> 00:04:36,370
if you speak the truth or not.

77
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:40,250
What's with this atmosphere?

78
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:44,210
Looks like that little flame was right.

79
00:04:45,350 --> 00:04:48,570
Sima Jiao truly likes me.

80
00:04:52,790 --> 00:04:53,690
Serene Vale's specialty.

81
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:55,940
It clears the mind. Try it.

82
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:09,620
He hardly seems injured.

83
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:13,370
This place is the Mindscape that person created.

84
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:14,860
In half a day,

85
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:17,300
it will vanish.

86
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,570
No wonder it never turns dark.

87
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,210
There are no pursuers either.

88
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:25,740
By the way,

89
00:05:26,350 --> 00:05:28,370
that master asked me to tell you

90
00:05:29,030 --> 00:05:31,570
that other Spirit Fire still exists.

91
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:32,890
What does that mean?

92
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:34,890
Shi Qianlv's Spirit Fire

93
00:05:35,150 --> 00:05:36,740
that he secretly raised

94
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,420
likely hasn't gone out.

95
00:05:39,030 --> 00:05:41,370
Why did Shi Qianlv raise it secretly?

96
00:05:41,790 --> 00:05:43,330
Isn't Spirit Fire

97
00:05:43,350 --> 00:05:44,370
only for the Sima clan?

98
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:45,860
Do you know

99
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:48,570
that the Sima clan once ascended?

100
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,540
It was recorded in Gengchen's history.

101
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,010
Years ago,

102
00:05:53,350 --> 00:05:55,500
many Sima powerful cultivators

103
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:57,540
ascended to immortality through tribulation.

104
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,010
Ascending to immortality

105
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:04,010
is just a joke.

106
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:07,180
Whenever an immortal ascended in the past,

107
00:06:08,150 --> 00:06:10,210
the world brimmed with spiritual energy.

108
00:06:11,350 --> 00:06:12,180
That I know.

109
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:16,010
Books say when immortals ascend,

110
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:18,210
the gate to the divine opens,

111
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:19,620
and spiritual energy flows into the mortal realm.

112
00:06:21,270 --> 00:06:22,450
The truth is

113
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,010
that those immortals

114
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,300
never reached the divine world.

115
00:06:27,590 --> 00:06:29,210
They dissolved into the world.

116
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:33,130
Their souls and flesh became pure spiritual energy

117
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:34,810
and returned to the world.

118
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:36,620
Now,

119
00:06:37,150 --> 00:06:39,940
Sima clan is near extinction.

120
00:06:40,710 --> 00:06:42,980
It is fate within the heavens

121
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:45,940
that wants to destroy the Sima clan.

122
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,940
No wonder the Eight Palaces

123
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,690
and the Shi family dared

124
00:06:51,710 --> 00:06:54,100
to scheme against the remnants of the Sima clan.

125
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,570
It's because they know...

126
00:06:55,590 --> 00:06:56,130
They know

127
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,980
the glory of ascension

128
00:06:59,790 --> 00:07:00,690
was all fake.

129
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:04,130
Except for the Sima clan,

130
00:07:05,470 --> 00:07:06,450
no one knows

131
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,540
the way to end the curse

132
00:07:09,320 --> 00:07:10,620
is by merging Spirit Fire.

133
00:07:13,350 --> 00:07:15,770
And you just revealed this secret to me?

134
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,980
I don't need to hide anything from you.

135
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:23,620
It seems

136
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,450
Shi Qianlv has learned this secret

137
00:07:26,150 --> 00:07:27,300
that bred his greed.

138
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,810
That's why he raised Spirit Fire to gain eternal life.

139
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,130
Right?

140
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:31,810
Yes.

141
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,740
He created Baifeng Mountain

142
00:07:34,470 --> 00:07:37,890
to seize Fengshan blood by a blood-swapping ritual.

143
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:40,860
That way, he could merge Spirit Fire.

144
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:42,420
But

145
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,500
I've destroyed Baifeng Mountain.

146
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,740
He probably can't sustain Spirit Fire.

147
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:48,690
But that old man said

148
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:51,250
Shi Qianlv's Spirit Fire still burns.

149
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:54,810
It means he hid Fengshan bloodline elsewhere.

150
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:57,540
Blood-swapping for eternal life?

151
00:07:58,230 --> 00:08:00,300
Shi Qianlv is bold indeed.

152
00:08:01,390 --> 00:08:04,420
Do you plan to kill him?

153
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:07,210
Killing him alone won't do.

154
00:08:08,910 --> 00:08:10,500
I will plant hidden fire in the nine spiritual peaks

155
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:12,130
that nourish the Shi family.

156
00:08:13,350 --> 00:08:15,370
When I find Shi Qianlv's Spirit Fire,

157
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:18,500
I will ignite the fuse of the spiritual peaks

158
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:23,540
and ruin the Shi family's century-old delusion.

159
00:08:24,030 --> 00:08:25,770
But you just woke up.

160
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:29,450
How about you get better first?

161
00:08:30,350 --> 00:08:31,740
I don't know medicine.

162
00:08:31,990 --> 00:08:33,210
If you collapse again,

163
00:08:33,230 --> 00:08:34,570
what if I can't save you?

164
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:35,810
It doesn't matter.

165
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:37,730
I have many ways

166
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:39,570
to ruin the Shi family.

167
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:43,610
As long as I don't wish it,

168
00:08:44,830 --> 00:08:46,060
no one can kill me.

169
00:08:48,280 --> 00:08:49,300
Then

170
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,180
do you still want to die?

171
00:08:56,710 --> 00:08:58,300
You tried so hard to save me,

172
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,970
so I'll stay alive.

173
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:07,380
Where do we go next?

174
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,380
We'll go to the Shi family.

175
00:09:28,630 --> 00:09:29,660
Madam Ye.

176
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:36,420
Madam Ye, what brings you here?

177
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:39,420
I came to ask

178
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,690
what you will do with Sima Jiao

179
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:44,540
if you find him.

180
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:47,610
I will once again seal him

181
00:09:48,110 --> 00:09:50,060
in Three Saints Mountain.

182
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:52,610
We need you to help us

183
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:56,090
in activating the sealing array.

184
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:01,810
Sect Master Shi.

185
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:05,970
You probably have other plans.

186
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:12,940
Why do you say this?

187
00:10:13,110 --> 00:10:16,570
Baifeng Mountain was your work.

188
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:18,490
I wonder

189
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,730
where all the Fengshan blood

190
00:10:22,590 --> 00:10:24,090
in the mountain went?

191
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,570
I wonder too.

192
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:32,420
Instead of telling these to other palace heads,

193
00:10:33,630 --> 00:10:34,970
why come to me?

194
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:37,490
What do you seek?

195
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:43,260
I want Sima Jiao's life.

196
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:49,090
I never thought

197
00:10:49,990 --> 00:10:52,140
you hate Sima Jiao

198
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:53,970
this much.

199
00:10:56,110 --> 00:10:57,570
But your action

200
00:10:58,830 --> 00:11:00,540
isn't for private revenge.

201
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,490
It's

202
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:06,380
to break the Immortal-Demon Barrier.

203
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:07,970
We both have secrets.

204
00:11:08,990 --> 00:11:10,330
No need to hide.

205
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,690
I'll only ask you one thing.

206
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:16,260
Do you mean to kill Sima Jiao?

207
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:23,300
I can work with you.

208
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:25,300
Whether it's to kill a person or to put out the fire.

209
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:26,490
But

210
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:30,780
what do I gain from doing this?

211
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:33,780
I'll keep

212
00:11:34,510 --> 00:11:35,780
Baifeng Mountain's matter confidential.

213
00:11:36,750 --> 00:11:37,810
That's what you gain.

214
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:48,300
Madam Ye.

215
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:52,330
I have plenty of ways to shut you up.

216
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:56,210
What use is any of this to me?

217
00:12:06,990 --> 00:12:08,210
Don't forget.

218
00:12:08,590 --> 00:12:10,210
My cultivation isn't as strong as yours,

219
00:12:11,590 --> 00:12:13,090
but I'm the mistress of a palace after all.

220
00:12:13,830 --> 00:12:14,900
I hope

221
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,330
you won't underestimate me.

222
00:12:18,710 --> 00:12:21,570
But you and I share the same goal,

223
00:12:22,470 --> 00:12:24,730
so why waste effort working against each other?

224
00:12:25,230 --> 00:12:26,060
Why don't we join forces?

225
00:12:27,590 --> 00:12:30,610
After it's done, we each take what we need.

226
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:37,140
I greatly admire your boldness.

227
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:43,540
I also hope you'll let me know

228
00:12:44,110 --> 00:12:45,420
as soon as you have news.

229
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,610
I also hope

230
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:49,020
you'll keep your word.

231
00:12:58,870 --> 00:12:59,610
Greetings, Aunt.

232
00:13:00,590 --> 00:13:01,690
Xu, no need for such formalities.

233
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:03,970
I was incompetent.

234
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:05,850
I disappointed Father.

235
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:07,380
That's why I disturbed you, Aunt.

236
00:13:08,040 --> 00:13:08,570
It's fine.

237
00:13:08,570 --> 00:13:09,630
[Shi Qiandu]

238
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:10,660
I entered seclusion

239
00:13:11,110 --> 00:13:12,570
to improve my cultivation

240
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:15,450
so that I can help your father.

241
00:13:16,160 --> 00:13:18,690
Capturing Sima Jiao as soon as possible

242
00:13:18,710 --> 00:13:19,780
is the top priority.

243
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:22,660
The destruction of Baifeng Mountain

244
00:13:23,560 --> 00:13:24,570
isn't your fault.

245
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:26,810
You don't need to blame yourself too much.

246
00:13:27,830 --> 00:13:28,690
Thank you, Aunt.

247
00:13:31,560 --> 00:13:32,780
All disciples, heed my command.

248
00:13:33,830 --> 00:13:36,180
Split into two groups and follow me and your young master

249
00:13:36,710 --> 00:13:38,210
to search for Sima Jiao.

250
00:13:38,590 --> 00:13:39,210
Yes.

251
00:13:40,260 --> 00:13:43,180
[Luo River Immortal District]

252
00:13:48,470 --> 00:13:49,210
Grandmaster.

253
00:13:50,710 --> 00:13:51,380
Sima Jiao.

254
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:54,180
Why can't these people see us

255
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,300
and why don't they run into us?

256
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:57,900
I concealed us with invisibility.

257
00:13:59,040 --> 00:14:00,300
These people are low in cultivation.

258
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:03,180
If they feel a strong aura,

259
00:14:03,710 --> 00:14:04,490
they will avoid it on their own.

260
00:14:09,110 --> 00:14:10,300
It still works even when you're injured?

261
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:11,540
Even if my serious injuries haven't healed,

262
00:14:12,110 --> 00:14:14,940
these people are far from my match.

263
00:14:16,510 --> 00:14:18,610
Why don't we just use the invisibility all the time?

264
00:14:20,040 --> 00:14:22,900
Invisibility consumes quite a lot of spiritual power.

265
00:14:23,830 --> 00:14:25,540
I can only maintain it for a brief moment.

266
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,020
Right.

267
00:14:27,990 --> 00:14:29,330
You're still badly injured.

268
00:14:29,990 --> 00:14:31,810
Various high-level spells have failed too.

269
00:14:32,830 --> 00:14:34,380
Let's keep a low profile.

270
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:35,900
After all, we're on the run,

271
00:14:36,230 --> 00:14:36,970
not on vacation.

272
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,970
You don't need to worry about these things.

273
00:14:45,350 --> 00:14:46,060
With me here,

274
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:48,380
wherever you go is a vacation.

275
00:14:50,870 --> 00:14:52,260
That's a bold statement.

276
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:58,180
By the way, where are we?

277
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:00,380
It feels more and more remote

278
00:15:01,040 --> 00:15:02,450
on the way here.

279
00:15:03,110 --> 00:15:03,970
Luo River Immortal District.

280
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:07,900
A district where ordinary people and cultivators live side by side.

281
00:15:09,510 --> 00:15:11,180
It's the most marginal area of Gengchen Celestial Palace.

282
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:13,180
No wonder these people

283
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,900
look like they don't know any spells.

